antly trying out new \"rides\". This includes creative planning, video shooting, WeChat content creation and Fashion Week feature reports. Each project is like a roller coaster in a theme park and the first time you \"play\" you feel fresh and excited, and as we play more and more times, we gain the experience and skills to become more advanced players. You will never get bored because there are always new projects and rides to try.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow do you describe your job to friends and family?\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eI work for one of the coolest companies in the world. I have a stage where I can do what I am good at, get my work seen by a lot of people and make a lot of awesome friends.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLunar New Year is approaching soon, what does this holiday mean to you and how do you plan to celebrate?\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eUsually I rarely have time to spend with my parents, so this Spring Festival I will spend a lot of time at home with them.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eReflecting on this past year, what is a project that you worked on that you are most proud of?\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eWithout a doubt, GQ MOTY. We set so many seemingly impossible goals with creativity and imagination and turned them into reality through teamwork and hard work. It's a wonderful feeling.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGQ Men of the Year concluded in China in December of 2023. How will this event contribute to the success and outreach of the brand and where it is headed in the future?\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eI would like to answer this question with three keywords, which are also the three valuable qualities that describe the GQ team.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eThe first word is \"creative\". Creativity is the lifeblood of all content. GQ MOTY gives us a great opportunity to boldly incorporate all kinds of interesting ideas. When we have a great idea, we never hesitate to share it with the team as soon as possible.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eThe second word is \"breakthrough\". In the process of preparing for GQ MOTY, one of the most common questions we asked ourselves was: \"How can we be different?\" with the event location, the red carpet, the video shooting, the live stream. We hope that every aspect of the event will break through, not only to set the benchmark, but also to set the precedent.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eThe third word is \"teamwork\". GQ has an amazing team that supports and trusts each other as a family. It is also because of teamwork that we can complete so many seemingly impossible tasks. It is such a blessing to be a member of this team.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTell us a little bit about your role in organizing the event and what can we hope to see from MOTY events in China in the future?\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eI am mainly responsible for the creative and content planning of GQ MOTY. During GQ MOTY, we produced more than 1,000 photos and short videos, including the short film \"No Time,\" the \"GQ MOTY Magic Night\" micro-movie, and more.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eWe already have some very exciting ideas for future MOTY events. But... I want to keep it a secret, so you can look forward to next year's surprises!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat was your favorite part of working on MOTY?\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eThe red carpet fascinated me. The red carpet itself is a live show so it is full of many uncertainties. And what we have to do is to present a \"perfect\" red carpet live streaming as much as possible through sufficient preparation. Before the official red carpet starts, we usually have more than a dozen rounds of rehearsals and simulations to constantly optimize the lighting design, position design, camera angle and so on. As each rehearsal goes on, watching the red carpet get better little by little is a very fulfilling process.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat can we expect to see from the brand in 2024?\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003e2024 will undoubtedly be a more challenging year but we believe that challenges and 