ue with this tradition for Lunar New Year!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eReflecting on 2023, what is a project that you worked on that you are most proud of?\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eIn 2023, Condé Nast China kicked off our top talent project. As a human resources business partner, I worked with different departments to identify each team's top talents and participated in discussions to promote the talent development plan. This is a very important project for the company to retain and develop talents. I am very proud to be part of it.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat is something you would like to do more of in 2024?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eFrom the company's perspective, we hope to have more outputs in new businesses. I hope that I can assist business departments achieve this goal successfully.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAs part of the HR team, how does Condé Nast China attract and retain top talent in the competitive media landscape?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eWe keep paying attention to both internal and external benchmarks so that we can maintain a competitive position in the market.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow does Condé Nast China foster a diverse and inclusive workplace? Cou