\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eThese awards are very special for the brand as they are a celebration of the entire industry. The credibility of these awards, the turnout and the respect engendered is a result of the painstaking work and dedication by the whole team. This is what makes it an award to be proud of, to hold up as an example and work for tirelessly.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow were the restaurants selected?\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eThe restaurants were selected across India via a complex process of longlisting, self nominations and voting by 100 jury members from around India which included food writers, critics and other prominent tastemakers. The voting process is then audited and tabulated by an independent consulting firm.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow are this year’s awards different from previous years?\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eThis year is even more special as the awards have returned after a three-year hiatus, bigger and better than ever. Emerging from the challenges of a global pandemic with more spunk, creativity than ever before, this year’s winners are a surprising list and point to the changes in the industry and the changing appetite and interests of diners.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCan you tell us what goes into making the Condé Nast Traveller Restaurant Awards a successful event and evening?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eThese are the most credible awards that matter to the industry. Everyone shows up, those who win and those who don't—to cheer their friends on. And above all, it’s a great party.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat do you hope to see in future awards for the brand?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eA similar support base, respect and a fabulous event that is remembered by all who attend.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWere there any surprises this year or any behind-the-scenes moments you can share?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eThere are plenty of surprises and they will be unveiled on the 9th! Our lips are sealed till then.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat was your favorite restaurant that won this year? Why?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\