estors to achieve freedom. In my opinion, Hispanic culture means inspiration of love, unity, colours and life.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat are some of the visual campaigns you have designed and which one are you most proud of?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003eI had the opportunity of designing the first campaign of the first Wired Summit in Mexico, the design of the 20\u003csup\u003eth\u003c/sup\u003e anniversary of AD’s logo in Mexico as well, such as Vogue celebrating Mexico’s Bicentenario and Vogue Collection sales of clothing supporting inclusion.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhere do you draw your creative inspiration from?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003eI like to observe everything around me, since my home is all around the world, I love to observe all that is trending. I find inspiration in people, such as in life.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat do you think the next big design trend will be?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003eVintage is gaining big weight on people, “past/old” becomes cool and memorable. People get proud of themselves and choose to be themselves wearing comfortable, colorful clothes without rules.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat is a project you would love to work on but haven’t done yet?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003eI’d love to participate in campaigns to raise people's awareness or conscience to be empathic, not only with other people, but with animals and our planet as well.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIf you could snap your fingers and become an expert in something, what would it be?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003eIf I could snap my fingers and do so, I’d become an expert in everything related to design, like illustration, photography and animation.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhen you’re not working, how do you spend your free time?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003eIn my spare time, I enjoy taking long walks and playing with my two chihuahua dogs. I also like taking pictures of them and if there’s still time, I love to go swimming.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTell us about your perfect Sunday.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003eMy perfect Sunday would be a day in which I’d take a walk in the early morning after having breakfast with my husband. Then I would go visit my family and have a meal with them in an outdoor place so I can take my dogs with us. Later, I’d have a cappuccino, take a walk again with my puppies and I’d watch a movie by the end of the day.\u003c/span\