3e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003eThis year we decided to give Vogue World a charitable mission, and in addition to private donations, are giving 100% of the post-tax ticket proceeds to various performing arts organizations in London.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCan you tell us what goes into creating such a large event like this?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003eI can’t think of a single department at Condé Nast that hasn’t touched this project.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhere do you hope to see Vogue World land next?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003eSooner or later, someone will do a fashion show in space.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat are you most excited about for Vogue World: London?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003eSurprising people! The idea is to refresh the format of Vogue World every year.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAdditional talent were recently announced, who are you most looking forward to seeing? Why?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003eStormzy’s performance, which features Sophie Okonedo, Vivienne Westwood, and Shakespeare. It’s the whole package.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWe have already seen Vogue World inspire the next generation of designers with the students from the \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://mcusercontent.com/4b3529414ef79e1b3850c49ea/files/ae6e20af-2819-6de4-e043-6aaa3acd6202/Fashion_High_School__New_York_Kids_Put_On_a_Glamorous_Runway_Show_The_New_York_Times_min.pdf\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#1155cc;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cu\u003eHigh School of Fashion Industries\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e. How did it feel to see such a huge impact?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003eThere is nothing more inspiring than realizing that you’ve inspired others.\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAre you able to share any behind the scenes moments with us either from this year or last year’s Vogue World?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\"\u003eLast year, there were storm warnings the entire week leading up to Vogue World, which was outdoors. We looked at backup venues in Brooklyn. Our dress rehearsal was interrupted by lightning. We had meteorologists and a weather shaman advising us, if you can believe it. But for two hours on the evening of September 12, the clouds cleared and we had perfect weather.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","publishedDate":"2023-09-11T11:00:00.000Z","isFeatured":false,"isHidden":false,"tag":null,"createdAt":"2023-10-09T02:19:54